    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document recommends that network implementors who have planned or deployed an OSI NSAP addressing plan, and who wish to deploy or transition to IPv6, should redesign a native IPv6 addressing plan to meet their needs.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
